# Scripts Reference

## Installation Scripts

### scripts/install-rhoai-33.sh (1100+ lines)
Full RHOAI 3.3 installation with all prerequisites.

**Usage:**
```bash
./scripts/install-rhoai-33.sh [OPTIONS]
  --skip-prerequisites    Skip NFD, GPU, Kueue, cert-manager
  --skip-rhcl            Skip RHCL/Kuadrant (no MaaS auth)
  --skip-maas            Skip MaaS configuration
  --skip-node-scaling    Skip automatic worker/GPU node scaling
  --no-llmd              Don't configure llm-d Gateway
  --channel <channel>    RHOAI channel (fast-3.x, stable-3.3)
  --domain <domain>      Cluster domain
  --timeout <seconds>    Wait timeout (default: 600)
```

**Installation Order:**
1. Check prerequisites (OCP 4.19+, cluster-admin)
2. Scale cluster nodes (workers to 2, create GPU machineset)
3. Install operators: NFD → GPU → Kueue → cert-manager → LWS
4. Install RHCL (Service Mesh 3 → Kuadrant → Istio → Authorino TLS)
5. Create inference gateways (maas-default-gateway, openshift-ai-inference)
6. Enable user workload monitoring
7. Install RHOAI operator (interactive channel selection)
8. Create DataScienceCluster
9. Enable dashboard features, create hardware profile

### scripts/install-rhoai-minimal.sh
